      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/2361842-the-haunted-mesa">Quotes from The Haunted Mesa</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Knowledge was not meant to be locked behind doors. It breathes best in the open air where all men can inhale its essence.&rdquo;</span>
